https://www.niuqi360.com/webmaster/how-to-get-a-google-translate-api-key/


In order to execute successfully, you need to get the API for deepl first.
Then populate the key into the arguments of the py file(deep_api_in.py).
'''
    params = {
        'q': text,
        'target': target_lang,
        'source': source_lang,
        'key': 'YOUR_API_KEY'  # replace with your Google Cloud API key
    }
'''




###############################################################
#################  中文 ########################################
###############################################################

为了执行成功，你需要先获取deepl的API，
然后将key填充到py文件(deep_api_in.py)的参数中。

    params = {
        'q': text,
        'target': target_lang,
        'source': source_lang,
        'key': 'YOUR_API_KEY'  # replace with your Google Cloud API key
    }